<p>It&#8217;s a nod to <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0390384/">&#8220;Primer&#8221; (2004)</a> (not a bad film to nod to), with some fantastic homebrew production design and great editing, and a tight, bite-sized story. Well done, friends.</p>
