<p>What, am I supposed to refrain from gushingly reblogging this? I&#8217;m super proud of you, is all. (That&#8217;s me, arguing with Roxana when she sees that I&#8217;ve reblogged this. And then she&#8217;s like &#8220;I don&#8217;t need favors from you&#8221; and I&#8217;m like &#8220;come on baby you know you can&#8217;t stay mad at me&#8221; and she&#8217;s like &#8220;stop having pretend conversations with me on your site, stu&#8221; because &#8220;stu&#8221; is short for &#8216;stupid&#8217;.)</p>
